Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpts] Helsinki has today celebrated the 50th 
anniversary of the air defense victory of the city. [passage 
omitted] In his speech at the main festivities, Admiral Jan 
Klenberg, commander of the Defense Forces, found many 
similarities between the current air defense of Helsinki and the 
air defense of 50 years ago. Klenberg said that the spirit of 
the air defense is still good. However, the commander of the 
Defense Forces emphasized that the missile system protecting the 
capital should be renewed. 

