<F P=100> AUSTRIA </F>
<H3> <TI>   `Pro-Serbian' Demonstrators Criticize Mock in Vienna </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU2802141594 Vienna DER STANDARD in German 28 Feb 94 p 3 </F>
<F P=103> AU2802141594 </F>
<F P=104>  Vienna DER STANDARD </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> German </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] According to the police, about 2,000 people 
demonstrated "against the suffering of the people in former 
Yugoslavia" in front of the parliament in Vienna on Sunday [27 
February]. The pro-Serbian demonstrators accused Foreign 
Minister Mock of "causing a third world war" with his policy. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

